name: Sun Painting 1
description:
A series of 18 watercolours, painted on Moleskine, 200-gram cold-pressed paper.

Paper Size (cm): 14 x 9. Framed size (cm) 30 x 24

Each painting is framed and mounted using the finest quality materials. 

Each work is available to buy as single paintings. 

To purchase as a series of 18 works, a discount of 10% would apply.

All purchased works will be delivered by postage (using Royal Mail - and include additional relevant costs). Works may be delivered by hand if local.
